We want to inform you that whenever you use our Service, in a case of an error in the App we collect data and information on your device called Log Data. This Log Data may include information such as your device Internet Protocol (‚ÄúIP‚Äù) address, device name, operating system version, the configuration of the app when utilizing our Service, the time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics.
